<div class="content_block"><h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>2300 Mt Olympus Dr, Los Angeles, CA 90046</strong></h2>
<br />

<p style="line-height:1.5em;">Multilevel Modern Architectural in the Hollywood Hills. Sleek and clean finishes characterize this 4 bed | 3.5 bath home with open spaces, high ceilings, LED recessed lighting and grand windows offering natural light and green views. Artistic and dramatic entryway showcase diverging angles and a beautiful staircase for those who appreciate design. Contemporary sunken formal living room with fireplace surrounded by white walls, large windows and two balconies framing the views of the forestry. Gorgeous custom glass chandelier dripping down from 12ft ceilings serving as a centerpiece for the private and elegant dining room. Galley Kitchen featuring Viking Appliances, seamless custom cabinetry and separate breakfast area. Relaxing top floor Master Retreat with stone wall fireplace, balcony and spacious walk in closet. Floating cabinetry, lighted mirrors, double sinks, double rain shower heads and standalone tub with green and lush views of the hills make up the lavish master bathroom.  Remaining sizable bedrooms on third level. Great outdoor living with large sitting areas on newly constructed mahogany deck, grassy backyard with BBQ and Jacuzzi- California lifestyle at its best!</p>

